Archlinux
=========

To build the package under Archlinux, grab the package tarball from the current
release[1] or the latest git version[2] and build the package with makepkg[3].

[1] http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=31518
[2] http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=31515
[3] http://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Makepkg


To ease things you could also install yaourt[4], which should automatically
download, build and install the package.

[4] http://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Yaourt
